        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "The result is cars that not only "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "look sleeker"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ", but also go faster, have better grip, and get better gas mileage. This wasn't always the case, though, and it didn't take long after the birth of the automobile for folks to begin experimenting with streamlined shapes."
